in\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We spend so much time away from our families because we do not have track in Ireland but it brings use closer together and we are really good mates because of it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2411, \"end\": 2418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9884460611117319, \"rank\": 0.009910658567694337, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much time\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"our families\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"use\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"good mates\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2481}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although they could not advance in the team pursuit, they are not done in Paris yet.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999904805463, \"rank\": 9.519419100674023e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team pursuit\", \"from\": 2534, \"to\": 2550}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gillespie will ride in Sunday's omnium, and also team up with Sharpe in theMadisonon Friday.\", \"from\": 2584, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2584, \"end\": 2593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Gillespie\", \"score\": 0.7090160454449259, \"rank\": 0.4104053165268076, \"text\": \"Gillespie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Gillespie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jason_Gillespie\"}, {\"begin\": 2646, \"end\": 2